OL,3,CBoy, 15, charged after school stabbing
OL,5,FA 15-year-old boy has been charged
OL,6,Fafter a stabbing at a Nottingham
OL,7,Fschool.
OL,9,FPolice were called to the attack at
OL,10,FNottingham University Academy of
OL,11,FScience and Technology in Dunkirk Road
OL,12,Fat 1.36pm on Thursday (5 March).
OL,14,FA 15-year-old boy was taken to
OL,15,Fhospital - where he remains with non-
OL,16,Flife-threatening injuries.
OL,18,FThe boy who has been charged, and who
OL,19,Fcannot be named because of his age, is
OL,20,Faccused of grievous bodily harm and
OL,21,Ftwo counts of possession of a knife.
