OL,3,CBoy, 15, charged after school stabbing
OL,5,FHe will appear at Nottingham
OL,6,FMagistrates Court on Monday (9 March).
OL,8,FDetective Chief Inspector Chris
OL,9,FBerryman, of Nottinghamshire Police,
OL,10,Fsaid: "This incident has
OL,11,Funderstandably been deeply upsetting
OL,12,Ffor students, teachers and the wider
OL,13,Fschool community.
OL,15,F"The victim's family, and others
OL,16,Faffected by what happened, are being
OL,17,Foffered support.
