OL,3,CBoy, 15, charged after school stabbing
OL,5,F"Detectives and uniformed officers
OL,6,Fhave worked quickly and I hope our
OL,7,Fresponse and these charges provide
OL,8,Fsome comfort to those impacted.
OL,10,F"We are grateful for the support of
OL,11,Fthe school and community during our
OL,12,Finvestigation."
